Column one
About Us
Fleetwood Mobile Home and RV Park
A Place to Call Home—Whether for a Short or Long Stay—in Central Jacksonville, Florida
Column one
Great Central Location
Fleetwood Mobile Home and RV Park is one of the only parks centrally located in Jacksonville, Florida. You’ll never run out of things to do and see with big city fun and coast excitement. Not to mention all the delicious restaurants, local grocery stores, employment opportunities, and so much more. Never be too far from everything you need! Book today.
Book Now
Column one
Community Setting for Long-Term and Short-Term Stay
Whether you’re a growing family, a retiree, a local employee, a student, or just looking for a short-term stay, our welcoming community is ready to create a space for you. Dedicated to resident comfort, Fleetwood Mobile Home and RV Park is a quiet neighborhood where everyone looks out for each other. Some residents have been here for over 19 years! Whether you need a place for a short visit or a long-term stay, enjoy the full-time community and care we offer today.
